715130f-a.text:
East 116th Street, east from Lexington Ave., showing a track removal project under way. Also shown are the Second and Third Ave. Elevated Lines upon their respective thoroughfares; the Third Ave. line showing one of its stations. The steeple shown is atop Grace P.E. Church, No.
212, south side, east of Third Ave.
January 4, 1937.
W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.
